Description:
Apartment Living In Style
An edgy new look has come to Dandenong in this bespoke new 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom corner ground floor apartment. Beautifully designed to capture an urban designer feel with custom cabinetry that maximises the space.
This quality-built abode features a vogue gallery-style kitchen with stone bench tops, pantry, north face living & dining opening to an alfresco. On offer there is also a stunning main bedroom (BIR & sleek ensuite) and double bedroom (BIR) along with European laundry and glamorous bathroom.
With a variety of great restaurants and shops sitting at your door, there's so much to love about the cosmopolitan feel and lifestyle that surrounds you, with Dandenong station and buses to get you where you need.
*** WHEN INSPECTING THE PROPERTY, PLEASE MEET OUTSIDE THE PROPERTY FACING HORNSBY STREET ***
Amenities nearby:
Dandenong Train Station
Accounting & Taxation Services
Automotive Mechanics (including Sheen Panel, Dandy Exhausts & DEA Performance)
Fish World Aquarium/Priority Pets
Doherty's Dandenong 24/7 Gym
Quick access to the M1 Freeway
Drum Theatre on Langhorne Street
Parkmore Shopping Centre & Dandenong Shopping Centre
Chisholm TAFE, Dandenong Library, Dandenong South Primary School & St Mary's Primary School

Description:
LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION!
We are proud to introduce this fantastic 4 bedroom home that is perfect for first home buyers, renovators, investors or developers with potential to build a second dwelling at the back of this existing home (STCA), fantastically situated on approx. 530 sqm, in a position that offers outstanding accessibility.
This property features four generously sized bedrooms, including a master which features a walk in robes and full ensuite, all secondary bedrooms are equipped with built in robes.
With unmatched luxury this home offers a separate family bathroom and kitchen plus a large family room that opens to a covered patio ideal for outdoor entertaining and a separate lounge & dining room for family gatherings.
Other features include Gas Heating, Split System Reverse Cycle Air Con and Solar electric system, also featuring a large driveway that has lots of parking space & provides access through double gates to the big backyard with tremendous potential to build another dwelling (stca).
A location such as this one is high in demand, with school like St Johns Regional College and Dandenong Primary School, Dandenong hospital, Dandenong market ,Tafe, train stations, bus tops, major freeways, Dandenong Plaza, shops, all short distance away. Nothing gets better than this when it comes to location.
Dont miss an opportunity to inspect this property in a highly sought out location, and call Shabana on 0411 216 186 or Khalil on 0421 711 125 before its too late!

Description:
Centrally located villa - no active body corporate!
Positioned in the heart of Dandenong, just minutes walk to shops, cafes and restaurants this location is perfect for a carefree lifestyle of convenience and low maintenance.
Well positioned at the rear of this friendly and secure block of units, this villa boasts a open floor-plan, a tiled entry leading to a lounge area with gas heating which opens into the kitchen with adjoining tiled meals area. Kitchen has plenty of bench and cupboard space with views into the courtyard garden area.
2 spacious, carpeted bedrooms both with built in robes and a central fully tiled bathroom with bath, shower and basin. The toilet is positioned between the bathroom and the separate laundry room.
There is dual internal access to the private courtyard garden plus a single brick garage also with courtyard entry. Extra parking is also readily available. With only 3 units in the group, there is no active body corporate.
A location of easy convenience with Dandenong Market, Plaza and train station all within minutes walk.

Upstairs the double sized master bedrooms can easily accommodate two double beds and has the convenience of a full ensuite and his & hers built in robes. The other two bedrooms are large and both feature built in robes and are serviced by a full family bathroom with toilet.

Description:
Huge family home in prime location!
Perfectly suited to a large family, this fantastic five-bedroom residence is ready to go. Simply move in and enjoy! Sitting pretty on an expansive 606m2 block, you'll benefit from a sizeable yard and a superb location that places you within minutes of shops, schools, public transport, the highway and hospital.
Showcasing an attractive exterior, this single-storey brick residence boasts a long driveway, landscaped front yard and charming lattice windows. As you step inside via the covered porch, you'll immediately spot the beautiful hardwood flooring which flows throughout. No carpets to vacuum here! The family room is located to your left and offers a bright, cosy space to relax at the end of the day. Nearby is the tiled dining area with adjoining kitchen. Fit for any aspiring chef, you'll find gas appliances, ample cabinets and a handy breakfast bar for mornings on the run.
A good-sized bedroom or second living area connects to the kitchen, while the other four bedrooms are zoned together with three including built-in robes. The generously-sized master enjoys its own exclusive en suite for complete privacy, while the updated family bathroom and separate WC serve the remaining bedrooms. Completing this comfortable abode is a laundry with exterior access, ducted heating for winter warming, pendant lighting and blinds/curtains throughout.
Stepping outside, you'll find the large rear yard which is perfect for the entire family, including the dog! There's plenty of room for outside toys, soaking up the sun and entertaining guests. To the front of the property, parking is completely covered by the larger-than-average single garage and roomy single carport.
When it comes to location, school drop-offs will be a breeze with several schools within walking distance. You're also within an easy stroll or short drive of the bustling Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Hospital, Dandenong Station, Melbourne Water Recreation Area and Dandenong Park. For speedy commutes or weekend road trips, several freeways and highways run close by.
This is a fabulous family home in a fast-growing location. Skip the queue. Call today! inspections are by appointment only.
